        {
            "title": "嘉泥近一年加碼台泥2.26萬張 持股比重增至5.09%緊追辜仲諒的5.26%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.WauCBAuyoloMm_JURoBXw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/cnyes_hk_559/40ce1a182d70f0cd387e7051b764103f\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
