        },
        {
            "title": "品牌與零售商:行銷版圖現況如何",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NcT6xOYN5fU9ZMUHoKQCEQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEB5A0UR_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong> 不斷變化的行銷版圖正迫使全球零售品牌和服裝公司重新思考其增長策略。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">德意志銀行分析師報告指出,整個板塊的新客戶獲取成本呈上升趨勢,預計這一主題將在2026年剩餘時間內主導董事會議程。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著企業需要在維持營收增長動能與在波動經濟中推動客流量的壓力之間取得平衡,預期結果將是行銷預算的全面增加,或至少是策略性調整。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>爭奪錢包份額的策略拉鋸戰</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">零售商目前面臨複雜的環境,高企的能源價格正在擠壓家庭預算,加劇了對消費者每一美元支出的爭奪。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-edc711c6-183b-3f19-a2d9-7130363f3b7c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第四季度財報公佈後,多家公司選擇優先進行品牌忠誠度再投資,這一決策雖然對長期健康發展必要,但暫時限制了利潤率。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師指出當前趨勢背後有三大主要驅動因素:市場領導者正加倍投入以保護其主導地位,表現不佳的品牌正爭相重獲相關性,而注重價值的零售商則積極開展活動,以在注重成本的購物者中保留錢包份額。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對投資者而言,影響深遠。那些主動投資於行銷基礎設施的公司現在被視為處於有利位置,能夠獲取增量市場份額。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">相反,那些歷來投資不足或現在才意識到需要資本提升以保持競爭力的公司,可能在試圖追趕日益擁擠且昂貴的數位廣告領域時面臨利潤率壓力。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>客戶獲取戰中的贏家與輸家</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不斷上升的獲取成本是整個板塊的逆風,但一些公司似乎比其他公司更能應對這種摩擦。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">德意志銀行指出結果存在明顯分歧。Birkenstock (BIRK)、Burlington (BURL)和Ross Stores (ROST)等公司被標記為行業範圍內行銷配置增加的潛在受益者。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時,Bath &amp; Body Works (BBWI)、Lululemon (LULU)、Nike (NKE)和Ulta Beauty (ULTA)等重量級企業可能被迫提高支出以維持其競爭優勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最終,被認為在這種環境下最具上行潛力的零售商包括American Eagle Outfitters (AS)、Five Below (FIVE)、Ralph Lauren (RL)和TJX Companies (<span><span>TJX</span></span>)。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些公司已經開始轉向主動的數據驅動投資,使它們即使在消費者注意力成本持續攀升的情況下仍能保持靈活。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E8%88%87%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%95%86-%E8%A1%8C%E9%8A%B7%E7%89%88%E5%9C%96%E7%8F%BE%E6%B3%81%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95-001952443.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-26 09:28:41",
